{"tid":1000093,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"急智口才究竟可以點練返黎？","createTime":"2019-01-29T07:51:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-29T08:59:01.000Z","uid":105507,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ae42e415132a73cf63902d019893634ebd12c517","tid":1000093,"uid":105507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T07:51:51.000Z","msg":"細細個嗰時覺得中文課好易咋嘛 我自己本身都係講緊中文寫既係中文字啦 有乜好學。相反依家諗返起中學做既英文卷只要你識啲生字夠多 做reading就一定攞高分 因為啲問題都係照直問照答。<br />\n愈大先知原來學中文係學佢既邏輯 語句間既鋪排 點樣講 用咩字眼可以講得鏗鏘有力 說服力強啲 用咩例子同比喻可以串到對方一棟都冇。<br />\n<br />\n人愈大要應付既人同事就愈黎愈多 中文好真係好多野易搞得掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">我都嫌我呢篇野表達得1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"c3f57b59e008628caa9cdcdc08b5fd9d93d4d3a8","tid":1000093,"uid":105507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T07:54:05.000Z","msg":"有時真係好羨慕啲有口才既人 尤其是啲律師臨危不亂仲可以轉數咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3355a8cff6e0b0fcc8d446eed792808b4818971f","tid":1000093,"uid":105507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T07:54:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79758f7a630c648a7dcf0c0a5a7ddd9d72eb88a8","tid":1000093,"uid":105507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T07:56:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c506024963936957e7724434b3e107da6ab09b38","tid":1000093,"uid":195815,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T07:57:05.000Z","msg":"上連登開秒回post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd771c85e03933cad4c49a3f5b8d24adb92e2651","tid":1000093,"uid":170375,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T07:58:01.000Z","msg":"首先玩cso<br />\n之後累死全家 你就會有口才<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 